<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c4">[ذرق]</span><a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c2">(ذَرَق)</span> الطائرُ <span class="c2">(يَذرِقُ)</span> بالضم والكسر <span class="c2">(ذَرْقاً)</span> سلَح. و <span class="c2">(الذَرْقُ)</span> السُلاح، تسميةً بالمصدر.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[[الذال مع العين]</span>]<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[ذعر]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">في حديث عمر <span class="special">﵁</span>:</span> «<span class="c2">(فذعرَها)</span> ذلك»<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أي خَوّفها إرسالُه إليها. و <span class="c2">(الذُّعر)</span> بالضم: الخَوف.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[ذعف]</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>يقال لسمّ الساعة <span class="c2">(١)</span>: سُمٌّ <span class="c2">(ذُعاف)</span>.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[[الذال مع الفاء]</span>]<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span><span class="c4">[ذفر]</span><a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c2">(الذِّفْرَى)</span> بالكسر: ما خَلْفَ الأُذن.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c2">(الذَفَرُ)</span>: ذكر في <span class="c2">(دف)</span>. <span class="c4">[دفر]</span>.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span><span class="c4">[ذفف]</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span><span class="c2">(ذَفَّف)</span> على الجريح، بالدال والذال، أسرَع قتْلَه. وفي كلام محمدٍ <span class="special">﵀</span> عبارةٌ عن إتمام القتل.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span><span class="c4">[[الذال مع الكاف]</span>]<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span><span class="c4">[ذكر]</span><a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>قطع <span class="c2">(مَذاكيرَهُ)</span>: إذا استأصل <span class="c2">(ذكَرَه)</span>. وإنما جُمع على ما حَوْلَه،<span class="c5"> كقولهم:</span> شابت مفارق رأسه.<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>و <span class="c2">(أذكَرت)</span> المرأةُ: ولدت <span class="c2">(ذُكوراً)</span>.<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span><span class="c5">وقول عمر:</span> <span class="c2">«هَبِلَت الوادِعيَّ أمُّه لقد أَذْكَرتْ به»</span><a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>أي جاءت به ذَكراً ذكيّاً داهياً.<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) سمي بذلك لأنه يقتل لساعته.</p> </div>